name: Don Kiki - Platinum Label - Grande
additionalNotes: Don Kiki cigars are recognized worldwide for their premium quality and taste. A Don Kiki cigar is always consistently good. Handmade in Esteli, Nicaragua by Master Cigar Maker Don Kiki Berger, they're considered a "Best Buy" when comparing them on quality and price. Available are the mild Don Kiki Green Label, the mild and opulent Don Kiki White Label from the Harvest of 2013, the medium-bodied Don Kiki Red Label and the full flavored Don Kiki Brown Label.
